<h2>My Favorite Music</h2>
<p>Sabrina Carpenter has neen one my favorite artists. Her song Espresso is the kind of track that just lives in your mind. It is catchy, confident, and impossible not to sing along to. Her style is fun and bold and her music always puts me in a good mood.
What makes Sabrina stand out is how much her music has grown over the years. She started out as a Disney actress but has fully stepped into her own as a pop artist. Her lyrics are clever and witty and she has a way of making every song feel personal.
Espresso in particular took over the summer and for good reason. The beat is light and breezy, the vocals are effortless, and it is the perfect song to have on repeat. If you have not listened to her latest album yet, it is absolutely worth checking out.</p>

